  "text": "where \u03b1 * denotes the optimal power allocation ratio that minimizes the hybrid outage probability P ho (\u03b1, R s ) in (18) (or equivalently, maximizes the secure transmission probability P st (\u03b1, R s ) in [CITATION_1] ) for a given R s . Mathematically, \u03b1 * is determined by",
